<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif text-primary">Health Checks</h1>
    <button class="btn-tonal"
            hx-target="#health-checks"
            hx-disabled-elt="this"
            hx-post="{{ url_for('health.refresh') }}"
            hx-indicator="#health-indicator">
        <icon>refresh</icon>Refresh
    </button>
</div>
{% include "health/timestamp.jinja" %}
<details class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-2 bg-surface-container-high rounded-md">
    <summary class="p-2 flex gap-2 items-center rounded-md bg-tertiary-container">
        <icon>help</icon>
        <span class="mr-auto">About health checks</span>
        <icon class="details-icon-open">keyboard_arrow_up</icon>
        <icon class="details-icon-closed">keyboard_arrow_down</icon>
    </summary>
    <div class="prose px-2 mx-auto">
        <p>
            These inspect the portfolio for issues, checking for anything that looks out of place.
            If there's a false positive, then click the hide button to ignore.
        </p>
        <p>Read about what each check specifically inspects for by expanding them.</p>
    </div>
</details>
<div id="health-checks" class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto">{% include "health/checks.jinja" %}</div>
